longBusinessSummary: GenCell Ltd. develops fuel cell solutions that offer clean power worldwide. The company's products include GenCell A5, an off-grid power solution for telecoms, schools, water purification, and other applications; GenCell G5rx, a utility backup power solution that produces 5kW of auxiliary electricity for substations during outages of any duration; and GenCell G5, a long-duration uninterruptible power supply that provides unlimited source of 5kW backup power for telecom, homeland security, healthcare, and industrial applications. It also provides GenCell IoT Remote Manager, a solution that supports backup power equipment in utilities, telecom, homeland security, healthcare, or industrial applications. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Petah Tikva, Israel.
